General.Name: Reinhold Europe AB
General.Description: Reinhold Europe AB (publ) provides real estate-related services. The company operates as a supplier/agent of prefabricated properties, including modules. It also constructs housing for senior citizens and permanent housing for immigrants; and develops prefabricated apartment modules for the construction of permanent or temporary housing. The company was formerly known as Reinhold Polska AB and changed its name to Reinhold Europe AB (publ) in May 2014. Reinhold Europe AB (publ) is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.
